---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../components/SectionDivider.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="About | RoboSoc" description="Learn about RoboSoc, the Robotics Society at the University of Exeter.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">About RoboSoc</h1>
      <p class="page-intro">
        RoboSoc (EXRS) is the Robotics Society at the University of Exeter. We bring together students who are passionate about building, programming, and learning about robots.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our mission</h2>
      <p>
        We exist to make robotics accessible to every student at Exeter, regardless of their background or experience level.
        Whether you are a Computer Science student who wants to work with hardware, an Engineering student exploring autonomy,
        or someone from a completely different discipline who is curious about robots, there is a place for you here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What we do</h2>
      <div class="activities-grid">
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Workshops</h3>
          <p>Hands-on sessions covering ROS 2, electronics, 3D printing, computer vision, and more. Beginner-friendly, always.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Build nights</h3>
          <p>Open lab sessions where we assemble robots, solder circuits, and iterate on designs together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Competitions</h3>
          <p>We enter teams into national and international robotics competitions, from line followers to autonomous challenges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Industry talks</h3>
          <p>Guest speakers from robotics companies and research labs share what it is like to work in the field.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="activity-card">
          <div class="activity-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Research</h3>
          <p>Collaborate on projects that explore real research questions, from SLAM to reinforcement learning for control.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our history</h2>
      <p>
        RoboSoc was founded in 2025 by Kazybek Khairulla, a Computer Science student at Exeter who saw a gap: there was no student society focused on building and programming robots. After getting the society officially recognised by the Exeter Students' Guild, the founding committee hit the ground running with workshops, build nights, and the society's first collaborative project.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        We are still in our first year, and everything is being built from scratch. That is what makes it exciting.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Affiliations</h2>
      <p>
        RoboSoc is a registered society under the <a href="https://www.exeterguild.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">University of Exeter Students' Guild</a>. We work closely with the Department of Computer Science and collaborate with university labs on hardware and research projects.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-title {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    max-width: 55ch;
  }

  .activities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 250px), 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .activity-card {
    background: var(--navy);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--card-radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .activity-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232, 116, 44, 0.08);
  }

  .activity-icon {
    color: var(--orange);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .activity-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .activity-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
